title: I Object!
itunes:title: I Object!
description:
Today on the show we took Angela Yee to Breakfast Club court after alleged comments on her being outside without a mask on after catching Covid during the week. Next, after Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a woman who played an "I object" prank at a wedding, we opened the phone lines to see if any of our listeners actually saw an objection at a wedding.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
